---
title: Smart Shawarma-Spiced Beyond Meat® Patties with Spinach Salad and Couscous
description: Beyond Meat® patties, packed with flavour-makers like shallots and Shawarma Spice Blend, are pan-fried to perfection in this recipe. Aromatic couscous and zingy garlic sauce ensure you don't sacrifice taste for calorie-and carb-consciousness.

